WEBVTT

00:00:35.930 --> 00:00:38.520
=Angels and Guards=

00:00:38.520 --> 00:00:41.270
=Episode 19=

00:00:42.375 --> 00:00:43.291
Hua. Bingfan.

00:00:43.750 --> 00:00:44.916
The Commander sent me to tell you.

00:00:45.375 --> 00:00:47.250
Word is, assassins from Liao
have entered the capital.

00:00:48.125 --> 00:00:49.583
Hua, we should go now.

00:00:49.916 --> 00:00:50.500
Duoyu.

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:52.458
Inform the Commissioner
and ask for backup.

00:00:52.875 --> 00:00:54.333
But if we deploy Jinyiwei now,

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:55.416
wouldn't that draw too much attention?

00:00:56.166 --> 00:00:57.583
Why not ask Guan Yunfeng

00:00:58.125 --> 00:00:59.333
and have the Enforcement Division help?

00:01:00.583 --> 00:01:01.083
Good point.

00:01:21.125 --> 00:01:22.250
I misjudged you earlier.

00:01:22.791 --> 00:01:24.625
And you even caught fish for me.

00:01:24.708 --> 00:01:25.375
I'm sorry.

00:01:26.291 --> 00:01:27.416
So you do know how to apologize.

00:01:28.083 --> 00:01:29.708
You ran so fast.
I could barely catch up.

00:01:30.416 --> 00:01:31.916
You scholars are so stubborn.

00:01:32.500 --> 00:01:33.625
I explained it over and over,

00:01:33.625 --> 00:01:34.416
and only then did you believe me.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:36.458
I have lived in the Ming Empire
for nearly ten years,

00:01:36.916 --> 00:01:39.166
yet I never knew the Northern Bureau
had female Jinyiwei.

00:01:39.583 --> 00:01:41.041
We were recruited in secret.

00:01:41.250 --> 00:01:42.375
That is why outsiders don't know.

00:01:42.625 --> 00:01:43.416
And you must not tell anyone.

00:01:43.958 --> 00:01:45.750
Miss Cheng, you seem so gentle
and refined.

00:01:46.916 --> 00:01:48.375
Why would you apply to be Jinyiwei?

00:01:48.875 --> 00:01:51.208
My mother died when I was little.

00:01:52.083 --> 00:01:53.833
Then my father married another woman.

00:01:54.541 --> 00:01:56.375
My stepmother was awful.

00:01:56.625 --> 00:01:57.625
She wanted to sell me

00:01:57.625 --> 00:01:58.875
to a very rich old eunuch.

00:01:59.875 --> 00:02:01.250
Luckily, I met Bingfan.

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:03.708
If I had not met her,

00:02:04.375 --> 00:02:05.750
who knows what would have happened?

00:02:06.708 --> 00:02:07.375
And just like that,

00:02:07.791 --> 00:02:09.333
I somehow ended up with the Jinyiwei.

00:02:09.500 --> 00:02:11.000
My father had many consorts.

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:13.291
My mother was never favored.

00:02:14.375 --> 00:02:15.625
I had eight older brothers.

00:02:16.041 --> 00:02:17.375
They called it studying in Ming,
your country.

00:02:18.250 --> 00:02:19.375
But I was clearly sent here
as a hostage.

00:02:20.458 --> 00:02:23.166
I haven't been home in ten years.

00:02:24.083 --> 00:02:25.291
Even when my mother died,

00:02:26.333 --> 00:02:28.041
I was not allowed to return
for her funeral.

00:02:29.500 --> 00:02:30.666
So princes

00:02:30.666 --> 00:02:32.500
and commoners like us

00:02:33.625 --> 00:02:34.458
don't live so differently after all.

00:02:34.958 --> 00:02:36.083
The rebellion in Liao

00:02:36.750 --> 00:02:37.750
had nothing to do with me.

00:02:38.833 --> 00:02:40.875
Now I'm the only card left to play.

00:02:42.416 --> 00:02:44.083
Ming wants to put me on the throne

00:02:44.375 --> 00:02:45.833
so it can keep control over Liao.

00:02:45.958 --> 00:02:46.833
Ten years ago,

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:48.708
no one cared about a useless man
like me.

00:02:49.625 --> 00:02:51.583
Now everyone wants to use me
as their pawn.

00:02:53.333 --> 00:02:54.000
Don't worry.

00:02:54.333 --> 00:02:56.083
The Northern Bureau is escorting you
this time.

00:02:56.333 --> 00:02:57.416
We will help you take back your throne.

00:02:58.541 --> 00:02:59.416
I don't want the throne.

00:03:00.541 --> 00:03:01.541
I don't want to be the King.

00:03:02.583 --> 00:03:03.958
I only want to live

00:03:05.250 --> 00:03:06.291
a simple life with the person I love.

00:03:06.791 --> 00:03:08.333
The person you love?

00:03:09.416 --> 00:03:10.458
You have someone you love?

00:03:11.500 --> 00:03:12.333
Before, I didn't.

00:03:13.416 --> 00:03:14.125
But now,

00:03:15.958 --> 00:03:16.541
I do.

00:03:35.583 --> 00:03:36.166
Xintian.

00:03:42.750 --> 00:03:43.750
Bingfan. Hua.

00:03:46.916 --> 00:03:49.333
It seems Liao's new ruler
wants Fa Yuanrong dead,

00:03:49.333 --> 00:03:50.875
even if it means offending Ming.

00:03:51.875 --> 00:03:54.125
He even sent assassins
into the capital.

00:03:54.541 --> 00:03:55.125
I think

00:03:55.583 --> 00:03:57.166
we shouldn't escort him back

00:03:57.166 --> 00:03:57.958
with a big show of force.

00:03:58.416 --> 00:03:59.333
We should travel in disguise

00:03:59.666 --> 00:04:01.125
and secretly take him to Yunnan.

00:04:01.458 --> 00:04:02.625
Hand him
to the Pacification Commissioner there.

00:04:03.541 --> 00:04:05.416
That would still complete our mission.

00:04:05.625 --> 00:04:06.208
I agree.

00:04:06.333 --> 00:04:08.166
If someone tips off the court

00:04:08.291 --> 00:04:09.208
that the Jinyiwei have moved,

00:04:09.708 --> 00:04:10.458
we will be in more trouble.

00:04:11.250 --> 00:04:12.416
I agree with going in secret.

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:14.166
But there is one problem.

00:04:14.666 --> 00:04:16.291
If danger comes,
we will have no backup.

00:04:19.208 --> 00:04:20.041
I can ask for leave

00:04:20.791 --> 00:04:21.625
and escort you along the way.

00:04:21.625 --> 00:04:21.958
No.

00:04:22.750 --> 00:04:24.000
You are a Ministry of Justice constable.

00:04:24.250 --> 00:04:25.041
Taking sudden leave

00:04:25.458 --> 00:04:26.541
would only raise suspicion.

00:04:27.750 --> 00:04:28.666
But I'm worried.

00:04:30.125 --> 00:04:30.958
Liao's new ruler

00:04:31.166 --> 00:04:32.791
will not rest until the Ninth Prince
is dead.

00:04:33.208 --> 00:04:34.500
If they dare strike in the capital,

00:04:35.375 --> 00:04:36.500
the road will be even more dangerous.

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:38.541
That is exactly why we go in secret.

00:04:40.083 --> 00:04:41.125
Too many people will expose us.

00:04:41.583 --> 00:04:43.208
If it's just the three of us
female Jinyiwei,

00:04:43.666 --> 00:04:44.708
we are less likely to draw suspicion.

00:04:47.208 --> 00:04:48.458
Then you must all be careful.

00:04:49.041 --> 00:04:49.416
Okay.

00:04:51.458 --> 00:04:53.250
We leave tomorrow

00:04:53.291 --> 00:04:54.666
to escort the Prince of Liao

00:04:54.750 --> 00:04:55.750
to the Yunnan border.

00:04:56.333 --> 00:04:56.833
I know.

00:04:58.000 --> 00:04:58.833
It is your mission.

00:04:59.416 --> 00:05:00.083
But

00:05:00.875 --> 00:05:01.916
there is something you should know.

00:05:03.291 --> 00:05:03.791
Go on.

00:05:04.458 --> 00:05:05.000
Someone

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.041
at court does not want
Fa Yuanrong to take the throne.

00:05:09.125 --> 00:05:10.000
So your mission

00:05:10.291 --> 00:05:11.625
may change at any moment.

00:05:15.000 --> 00:05:16.666
But these are the orders we have.

00:05:17.666 --> 00:05:19.958
So I have to carry them out.

00:05:25.083 --> 00:05:25.666
I will wait for your return.

00:05:30.060 --> 00:05:32.930
(Chong'er Pavilion)

00:05:44.791 --> 00:05:45.541
Bingfan.

00:05:46.375 --> 00:05:48.166
Be very careful on this journey.

00:05:48.583 --> 00:05:51.166
If anything happens on the road,

00:05:52.083 --> 00:05:54.125
take my command badge

00:05:54.875 --> 00:05:57.750
and seek help
from the local authorities.

00:06:03.375 --> 00:06:04.125
Understood.

00:06:10.333 --> 00:06:10.666
Give it to me.

00:06:12.916 --> 00:06:14.000
It may save you when it matters.

00:06:17.470 --> 00:06:22.390
♪Drowning in your world♪

00:06:23.180 --> 00:06:28.680
♪I ask myself before I can wake♪

00:06:29.083 --> 00:06:29.708
I came to see you off.

00:06:30.041 --> 00:06:31.125
Please be careful on the road.

00:06:31.458 --> 00:06:32.291
If you run into danger,

00:06:32.625 --> 00:06:33.375
send me word by carrier pigeon.

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:39.000
So you can travel all that way
to collect her body?

00:06:39.875 --> 00:06:40.500
What are you talking about?

00:06:41.083 --> 00:06:41.833
Don't jinx it.

00:06:44.750 --> 00:06:46.791
Young Master Chang and Duoyu
didn't come?

00:06:47.458 --> 00:06:50.875
Exactly. Always being so nice to us,

00:06:51.208 --> 00:06:53.000
but they're gone when it matters.

00:06:54.291 --> 00:06:56.041
I said goodbye to Young Master Chang
yesterday.

00:06:56.750 --> 00:06:58.250
It's getting late. Let's go.

00:07:43.500 --> 00:07:44.541
You must be exhausted.

00:07:45.500 --> 00:07:46.166
I'm fine.

00:07:46.541 --> 00:07:48.208
Have some mung bean soup.
It will cool you down.

00:07:49.083 --> 00:07:50.166
You even packed mung bean soup?

00:07:51.125 --> 00:07:52.333
Xintian, you are so thoughtful.

00:08:04.250 --> 00:08:05.541
Hua. Bingfan.

00:08:12.916 --> 00:08:14.041
Hua. Bingfan.

00:08:14.750 --> 00:08:15.708
Duoyu.

00:08:16.125 --> 00:08:16.958
What are you doing here?

00:08:18.166 --> 00:08:19.583
I want to go to Yunnan with you.

00:08:19.875 --> 00:08:20.416
Absolutely not.

00:08:21.083 --> 00:08:22.750
We left Chang Beiming
and Guan Yunfeng behind.

00:08:22.833 --> 00:08:23.583
What could you possibly do?

00:08:23.666 --> 00:08:24.083
I...

00:08:24.208 --> 00:08:24.666
Exactly.

00:08:25.291 --> 00:08:26.791
You cannot fight at all.

00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:28.375
Go back to the Errand Office.

00:08:28.666 --> 00:08:30.500
The road out there is dangerous.

00:08:31.083 --> 00:08:32.291
I can't fight,

00:08:32.541 --> 00:08:34.291
but I can think on my feet.

00:08:34.666 --> 00:08:36.250
And I'm good at making plans.

00:08:40.083 --> 00:08:42.083
Maybe we should take him.

00:08:42.333 --> 00:08:43.875
He is good with gadgets.

00:08:44.125 --> 00:08:46.166
He may come in handy.

00:08:47.291 --> 00:08:48.083
Fine.

00:08:48.083 --> 00:08:48.875
Hyah!

00:08:49.333 --> 00:08:50.125
Hyah!

00:08:50.291 --> 00:08:50.666
Hyah!

00:08:58.430 --> 00:09:05.310
(Prince Fa Yuanrong
of the Kingdom of Liao)

00:09:13.416 --> 00:09:15.416
An envoy of Liao comes by order
of the new king

00:09:15.625 --> 00:09:17.000
to meet the third-ranked man

00:09:17.250 --> 00:09:19.541
on the Central Plains Bounty List,

00:09:20.041 --> 00:09:21.125
Tuba Zangxi, the Smiling Yama.

00:09:22.750 --> 00:09:25.708
An envoy of Liao comes
to my hell on earth.

00:09:26.791 --> 00:09:28.458
What business brings you here?

00:09:29.041 --> 00:09:32.375
Our King knows you deal in lives.

00:09:33.458 --> 00:09:34.958
He has a rich job for you.

00:09:35.083 --> 00:09:35.666
I wonder

00:09:36.041 --> 00:09:37.750
if you are interested.

00:09:38.458 --> 00:09:40.708
The Hall of Yama takes lives for silver.

00:09:41.041 --> 00:09:42.125
Fair price. Clean deal.

00:09:42.708 --> 00:09:45.791
(Tuba Zangxi, Third on the Bounty List)
Who does Liao's new King want dead?

00:09:45.833 --> 00:09:46.708
The Ninth Prince.

00:09:47.041 --> 00:09:48.000
Fa Yuanrong.

00:09:48.666 --> 00:09:50.166
Fa Yuanrong?

00:09:51.458 --> 00:09:53.541
Royal blood

00:09:54.458 --> 00:09:56.083
does not come cheap.

00:10:05.500 --> 00:10:05.958
Good.

00:10:06.541 --> 00:10:07.333
The Hall of Yama

00:10:07.916 --> 00:10:09.083
will take the job.

00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:23.583
My lord, a secret report just came in.

00:10:23.875 --> 00:10:24.458
Liao's new king

00:10:24.708 --> 00:10:25.708
has hired Tuba Zangxi

00:10:26.083 --> 00:10:27.041
to stop Fa Yuanrong

00:10:27.041 --> 00:10:27.791
from returning home.

00:10:27.833 --> 00:10:28.666
He ranks third on the Bounty List.

00:10:28.958 --> 00:10:30.000
Tuba Zangxi's killers

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:30.833
have all set out

00:10:31.458 --> 00:10:32.041
straight for Yunnan.

00:10:33.291 --> 00:10:33.958
So,

00:10:34.625 --> 00:10:35.750
both the court

00:10:36.250 --> 00:10:39.083
and the underworld
want the Ninth Prince dead.

00:10:40.125 --> 00:10:40.458
My lord.

00:10:40.833 --> 00:10:42.833
Then our three female Jinyiwei...

00:10:43.125 --> 00:10:43.916
Send a pigeon.

00:10:44.833 --> 00:10:46.083
Tell them to hand Fa Yuanrong

00:10:46.083 --> 00:10:47.625
over to the Governor of Yunnan

00:10:47.958 --> 00:10:49.208
and return at once.

00:10:49.666 --> 00:10:50.625
You mean

00:10:51.416 --> 00:10:52.041
we are no longer

00:10:52.416 --> 00:10:54.416
protecting the prince of Liao?

00:10:54.583 --> 00:10:55.916
To the court,

00:10:56.750 --> 00:10:58.208
Fa Yuanrong

00:10:59.875 --> 00:11:00.541
has outlived his use.

00:11:06.750 --> 00:11:09.333
Tell Bingfan and the others
to return quickly.

00:11:09.666 --> 00:11:12.250
Let's hope we are not too late.

00:12:20.208 --> 00:12:20.833
Duoyu.

00:12:21.208 --> 00:12:23.083
I packed some pastries. Try some.

00:12:23.208 --> 00:12:24.833
Hua, it is a long journey.

00:12:24.958 --> 00:12:26.083
Keep them for yourself.

00:12:31.958 --> 00:12:33.375
We are almost in Yunnan.

00:12:34.083 --> 00:12:35.291
May I step out for some air?

00:12:35.916 --> 00:12:37.708
Yuanrong, not yet.

00:12:38.166 --> 00:12:39.291
Your identity is too sensitive.

00:12:39.291 --> 00:12:40.375
It is too dangerous.

00:12:40.708 --> 00:12:42.083
Wait a little longer, all right?

00:13:00.208 --> 00:13:01.791
(Order from the Commander
of the Northern Bureau.)

00:13:02.208 --> 00:13:03.041
(Proceed to the relay station.)

00:13:03.500 --> 00:13:04.375
(Hand Fa Yuanrong)

00:13:04.583 --> 00:13:06.916
(over to the men sent
by the Governor of Yunnan.)

00:13:07.250 --> 00:13:08.041
(Don't fail.)

00:13:10.041 --> 00:13:11.375
It is the Commander's written order.

00:13:11.375 --> 00:13:12.500
He wants us to hurry
to the relay station

00:13:12.833 --> 00:13:13.750
and hand Fa Yuanrong over

00:13:14.000 --> 00:13:15.083
to the Governor of Yunnan's men.

00:13:16.000 --> 00:13:17.458
Weren't we taking him to the border?

00:13:18.333 --> 00:13:20.500
Now we hand him over
to the Governor of Yunnan?

00:13:20.666 --> 00:13:21.166
I don't know.

00:13:22.083 --> 00:13:23.583
But since it is the Commander's order,

00:13:23.875 --> 00:13:24.750
we do as we are told.

00:13:26.000 --> 00:13:28.083
Duoyu, where are we now?

00:13:28.625 --> 00:13:30.458
Three to five li from Yunnan territory.

00:13:31.000 --> 00:13:32.208
Then let's hurry.

00:13:40.541 --> 00:13:42.958
(Young Master! Young Master!)

00:13:43.666 --> 00:13:44.625
(Young Master Ye Ping sent this.)

00:13:44.625 --> 00:13:45.750
(A copy of a Cabinet memorial.)

00:13:46.520 --> 00:13:48.810
(A copy of a Cabinet memorial.)

00:13:52.333 --> 00:13:54.166
(They really are abandoning
Fa Yuanrong.)

00:13:57.208 --> 00:13:57.750
(Young Master Chang.)

00:13:59.916 --> 00:14:00.791
(Our contacts say)

00:14:01.041 --> 00:14:02.208
(Liao's new King paid a fortune)

00:14:02.250 --> 00:14:03.625
(to have Tuba Zangxi kill Fa Yuanrong.)

00:14:04.125 --> 00:14:05.000
(For that money,)

00:14:05.208 --> 00:14:05.958
(Tuba Zangxi has sent)

00:14:05.958 --> 00:14:06.750
(all his killers.)

00:14:07.500 --> 00:14:08.125
(Saddle the horses.)

00:14:12.583 --> 00:14:13.125
Hyah!

00:14:14.375 --> 00:14:14.833
Hyah!

00:14:20.875 --> 00:14:21.750
Are you sure you are coming?

00:14:22.625 --> 00:14:23.458
I'm doing this for Bingfan.

00:14:24.625 --> 00:14:25.791
Then let's see who gets there first.

00:14:30.958 --> 00:14:31.708
Who are you?

00:14:33.333 --> 00:14:35.416
Baihu Shen Bingfan of the Jinyiwei
Northern Bureau.

00:14:35.416 --> 00:14:36.791
I'm under orders to escort
the Prince of Liao

00:14:36.791 --> 00:14:37.791
and complete the handover here.

00:14:38.750 --> 00:14:39.291
Wait here.

00:14:47.970 --> 00:14:50.916
(Relay Station)

00:14:50.916 --> 00:14:52.208
(Relay Station)
I'm Qianhu Cao Ming

00:14:52.333 --> 00:14:53.333
from the Yunnan Governor's Office.

00:14:53.791 --> 00:14:54.791
Greetings, officers.

00:14:56.125 --> 00:14:57.125
Greetings, Qianhu Cao.

00:14:57.791 --> 00:14:59.041
Where is the Prince of Liao?

00:15:00.000 --> 00:15:00.583
Here.

00:15:09.291 --> 00:15:11.708
Baihu Shen, please hand
Prince Yuanrong over to me.

00:15:12.208 --> 00:15:13.041
We will handle

00:15:13.083 --> 00:15:14.458
everything from here.

00:15:15.375 --> 00:15:16.958
We need to complete the handover papers.

00:15:17.250 --> 00:15:17.833
Of course.

00:15:18.166 --> 00:15:19.291
This way, Officer Shen.

00:15:20.458 --> 00:15:21.000
Wait.

00:15:22.583 --> 00:15:23.875
Baihu Shen will come in with me

00:15:23.875 --> 00:15:25.333
to finish the handover.

00:15:26.125 --> 00:15:27.166
No one else may enter

00:15:27.541 --> 00:15:28.750
the relay station without orders.

00:15:29.041 --> 00:15:29.750
Why not?

00:15:30.416 --> 00:15:31.500
This is an imperial relay station.

00:15:31.791 --> 00:15:32.791
Why can't we enter?

00:15:33.000 --> 00:15:34.791
These are unusual times.
Please understand.

00:15:35.833 --> 00:15:37.125
Baihu Shen, please.

00:15:40.583 --> 00:15:41.250
Yuanrong.

00:15:42.416 --> 00:15:43.916
I suppose this is as far
as I can take you.

00:15:45.666 --> 00:15:46.416
Xintian.

00:15:47.125 --> 00:15:48.375
When I return home
and take back my throne,

00:15:48.791 --> 00:15:50.041
I will send someone to Ming for you.

00:15:52.458 --> 00:15:53.750
Take care of yourself.

00:15:54.083 --> 00:15:55.250
I hope you take back your throne.

00:16:03.958 --> 00:16:04.666
The handover is complete.

00:16:05.100 --> 00:16:06.470
(Northern Bureau Transfer Document)

00:16:07.875 --> 00:16:08.666
Prince Yuanrong,

00:16:09.083 --> 00:16:10.500
please rest inside the relay station.

00:16:43.041 --> 00:16:43.833
Xintian.

00:16:44.625 --> 00:16:45.333
Wait for me.

00:16:53.250 --> 00:16:54.333
Take care of yourself.

00:17:08.890 --> 00:17:09.680
(Northern Bureau Transfer Document)

00:17:12.791 --> 00:17:13.583
What are you thinking?

00:17:17.208 --> 00:17:18.250
That was too easy.

00:17:18.416 --> 00:17:19.458
Too smooth.

00:17:20.416 --> 00:17:21.166
Too...

00:17:22.708 --> 00:17:24.375
Too careless?

00:17:24.625 --> 00:17:27.000
For something as important
as handing over the Prince of Liao,

00:17:27.666 --> 00:17:28.333
the Governor of Yunnan

00:17:28.333 --> 00:17:29.458
should have come in person.

00:17:30.500 --> 00:17:32.500
Why send a mere Qianhu

00:17:32.708 --> 00:17:34.000
to sign the handover papers?

00:17:34.666 --> 00:17:36.166
Isn't he afraid
that something will go wrong,

00:17:36.375 --> 00:17:37.625
and he will be held responsible?

00:17:38.083 --> 00:17:38.958
And also,

00:17:39.416 --> 00:17:40.875
we came all this way,

00:17:41.166 --> 00:17:42.875
yet they wouldn't even let us
enter the station.

00:17:43.416 --> 00:17:45.250
They practically marched
Fa Yuanrong in like a prisoner.

00:17:45.708 --> 00:17:48.291
None of this feels right.

00:17:49.791 --> 00:17:50.708
Did you notice?

00:17:51.083 --> 00:17:52.958
The men guarding the station
were not relay officers.

00:17:53.500 --> 00:17:55.375
They were guards
from the Governor's Office.

00:17:55.750 --> 00:17:57.375
And when they took the Prince of Liao,

00:17:57.916 --> 00:17:59.583
their eyes were full of killing intent.

00:18:01.208 --> 00:18:01.708
Hua.

00:18:02.708 --> 00:18:03.500
Could they be

00:18:04.291 --> 00:18:05.500
fake soldiers?

00:18:05.500 --> 00:18:06.250
Fake?

00:18:07.291 --> 00:18:08.458
I don't think so.

00:18:09.291 --> 00:18:10.083
But

00:18:10.666 --> 00:18:11.958
they are definitely up to no good.

00:18:16.583 --> 00:18:17.500
What is it, Xintian?

00:18:18.791 --> 00:18:19.416
Bingfan.

00:18:19.958 --> 00:18:21.583
I suddenly have a terrible feeling.

00:18:22.250 --> 00:18:23.291
I feel like...

00:18:23.750 --> 00:18:24.333
I feel like

00:18:25.208 --> 00:18:26.583
something happened to Yuanrong.

00:18:26.875 --> 00:18:28.250
Should we go back and check?

00:18:46.970 --> 00:18:50.140
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

00:18:50.510 --> 00:18:53.890
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

00:18:54.140 --> 00:18:57.140
♪My heart drifted lost♪

00:18:57.140 --> 00:19:00.550
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

00:19:01.640 --> 00:19:04.850
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

00:19:05.260 --> 00:19:08.600
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

00:19:09.180 --> 00:19:11.390
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

00:19:11.390 --> 00:19:15.430
♪I've softly let it go♪

00:19:15.430 --> 00:19:19.300
♪The vow you made was true♪

00:19:19.300 --> 00:19:23.050
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

00:19:23.350 --> 00:19:25.260
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

00:19:25.260 --> 00:19:29.800
♪And forget at world's end♪

00:19:30.100 --> 00:19:31.600
♪Embracing memory♪

00:19:31.600 --> 00:19:33.970
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

00:19:33.970 --> 00:19:37.850
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

00:19:37.850 --> 00:19:40.180
♪I wish to let it pass♪

00:19:40.180 --> 00:19:45.180
♪And run toward this vast life♪